--------- About Us ----------
1) Add to urls.py:

path('aboutus', views.aboutus, name='aboutus'),

2) Add to views.py: 

	def aboutus(request):
   return render(request,
                 'bookMng/aboutus.html',
                 {
                     'item_list': MainMenu.objects.all()
                 })


